{"tid":1384923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍灣半島九巴衝上行人路 撞向外牆牆身凹陷","createTime":"2019-07-30T03:25:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T05:18:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"93bcb1bf65a4b17178ae9cc763610b72e99ee696","tid":1384923,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190730/_2019073008480126125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190730%2F_2019073008480126125.jpg&h=a5a25570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藍灣半島九巴衝上行人路，撞向外牆牆身凹陷。Tsz Hin Chan&lrm;圖片<br />\n<br />\n一輛118號九巴在藍灣半島巴士站出口衝上行人路，撞向商場外牆，牆身出現凹陷，有欄杆被撞毀。警方及救護員到場，47歲姓彭巴士司機報稱受傷，由救護車送院治理。警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，涉事巴士當時擬左轉，惟車長誤將油門當腳掣，巴士意外衝上行人路，再撞牆。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1555686/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%97%8D%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%8A%E5%B3%B6%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E8%A1%9D%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%B7%AF-%E6%92%9E%E5%90%91%E5%A4%96%E7%89%86%E7%89%86%E8%BA%AB%E5%87%B9%E9%99%B7</code></pre>"},{"pid":"5497826f56f7aff3fe443e80ec4d8eee8c7fa76f","tid":1384923,"uid":25183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:26:06.000Z","msg":"咁既情況，巴士佬係唔係都只需賠三百蚊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36893c76987a28e95519450e1c1e5ef49321d8c","tid":1384923,"uid":199062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:26:14.000Z","msg":"司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c97c1de797423d113532ddd8897cea1a9b0aba3","tid":1384923,"uid":5419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:01:13.000Z","msg":"罷工？"},{"pid":"9144cdf305bfaf47c7a4af7a475c49bb77e82b01","tid":1384923,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5497826f56f7aff3fe443e80ec4d8eee8c7fa76f","tid":138492